# signoz_notification_channel (Resource)

Creates and manages alertmanager notification channels in SigNoz.

~> **Phase 2 scope:** only `slack_configs` is supported. Configuring `email_configs`, `pagerduty_configs`, `opsgenie_configs`, `webhook_configs`, `discord_configs`, `msteams_configs`, `mattermost_configs`, `pushover_configs`, `telegram_configs`, `victorops_configs`, `webex_configs`, `wechat_configs`, `rocketchat_configs`, `sns_configs`, `incidentio_configs`, or `jira_configs` will fail at apply with an "unsupported channel type" error from the convertor. These attributes appear in the schema for forward-compatibility but are not wired through.

